(1, NULL, 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.', 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum', '1', '1', 1, NULL, '2022-07-06 01:05:21', '2023-06-27 10:21:29'),
(2, NULL, 'Question 2', 'Answer 2', '1', NULL, 1, NULL, '2022-07-06 01:05:39', '2022-07-06 01:05:39'),
(3, NULL, 'adadfsfgasdgsdfgsdfg sdfg', 'dasdas', '1', '1', 2, NULL, '2023-01-18 08:32:08', '2023-08-16 08:49:13'),
(4, NULL, 'What is Trade25?', 'Greek mathematician Archimedes had the first ever documented ‘Eureka’ moment whilst in the bath.\r\nSimilarly, Nick had his moment in the shower when he realised that there was a business opportunity in offering trade prices on garden and homeware products to the general public.\r\nSo, like any top bloke would do, he got his tradie mates together to form the beginnings of Trade 25.\r\nThe philosophy is simple. Businesses want to sell their stuff and people want to buy it, so why not sell more stuff to more people?\r\n\r\nT25 is a revolution in buying and selling. It takes the discounted pricing historically enjoyed only by the trades and offers the same to its members.\r\nWith trade prices significantly lower than recommended retail, T25 is creating a shift in the way we buy and sell whilst offering transparent discounts and savings on genuine and quality products to our members.', '1', '1', 1, NULL, '2023-02-27 10:20:01', '2023-04-06 04:23:45'),
(5, NULL, 'Maintainace of the system done by the equipment', 'Maintainace of the system Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.', '1', NULL, 1, NULL, '2023-08-10 09:42:21', '2023-08-10 09:42:21');
