(61, '63f73db976884', 'PRO000061', 47, 'Fencing test', '<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Information</h6>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"common-list\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; list-style-type: none; max-width: 628px; color: rgb(63, 55, 77); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); position: relative; padding-left: 16px;\">A durable, non yellowing, water based interior/exterior enamel that is low odour and easy water wash up.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Features</h6>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"common-list\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; list-style-type: none; max-width: 628px; color: rgb(63, 55, 77); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); position: relative; padding-left: 16px;\">Water based</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); position: relative; padding-left: 16px;\">Fast drying, 2 hour dry time</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); position: relative; padding-left: 16px;\">Available in 1L, 2L, 4L, 10L</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(80, 80, 80); position: relative; padding-left: 16px;\">Available in White, Deep, Ultra Deep and Extra Bright bases</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Warranty</h6>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(105, 95, 112); max-width: 628px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">All surfaces must be thoroughly cleaned and free of all loose dirt, dust, grease, loose or flaking paint, and loose surface plaster. Efflorescence or mould on masonry or concrete surfaces must be treated. Flatten gloss surfaces by thoroughly sanding and wipe clean with a damp cloth, then apply primer, sealer or undercoat as required. Do not sand between coats.</p>\r\n\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 12px; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Uses</h6>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(105, 95, 112); max-width: 628px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Dulux Aquanamel is a waterbased interior/exterior enamel that dries to a chip resistant, tough finish. Dulux Aquanamel can be used in many of the areas that traditional solvent based enamels are used, with all the time saving benefits of a water based paint. Dulux Aquanamel is non-yellowing and resists chipping. Dulux Aquanamel is highly recommended for doors, architraves, skirting boards, windows, timber trim and walls and is ideal for bathrooms, kitchens and laundries.</p>', 'Fencing Description', 31, '16781931826192.png', NULL, '16771475776293.pdf', 890, 750, 0, 16, 1, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-23 04:49:37', '2023-08-01 10:50:38'),
