(97, '64816066ca0da', 'PRO000097', 192, 'Asian paint', '<p>Asian Paints is India&#39;s leading paint and decor company and ranked among the top ten Decorative coatings companies in the world with a consolidated turnover of ₹ 345 billion. The company is ranked 2nd in Asia and 7th amongst the top coating&#39;s companies in the world.</p>', 'Asian Paints is India\'s leading paint and decor company and ranked among the top ten Decorative coatings companies in the world with a consolidated turnover of ₹ 345 billion.', 26, '16862004227362.jpg', NULL, '16862004225541.pdf', 10000, 9000, 1, 56, 1, 1, 1, '2023-06-08 05:00:22', '2023-08-17 07:39:26');
